  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e6be890c8a758f3488227c7687955d0c, type: 3}
  m_Name: PogoUnlock
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::TaleStoneData
  DialogueLines:
  - textVI: "S\u1EF1 s\u1EAFc nh\u1ECDn v\xF4 t\xECnh c\u1EE7a khu r\u1EEBng \u0111\xE3
      c\u1EAFn nu\u1ED1t bi\u1EBFt bao hy v\u1ECDng... nh\u01B0ng s\u1EF1 t\u1EADn
      c\xF9ng c\u1EE7a nguy hi\u1EC3m, c\u0169ng ch\xEDnh l\xE0 kh\u1EDFi \u0111\u1EA7u
      c\u1EE7a s\u1EF1 th\u0103ng hoa."
    textEN: The callous sharpness of the forest has devoured endless hopes... yet
      the depth of peril is but the birth of ascension.
    AutoSkip: 0
  - textVI: "K\u1EBB b\xE9 nh\u1ECF... \u0111\u1EEBng s\u1EE3 h\xE3i nh\u1EEFng m\u0169i
      nh\u1ECDn kia. H\xE3y r\xE8n \u0111\xF4i ch\xE2n th\xE0nh \xFD ch\xED s\u1EAFt
      \u0111\xE1, v\xE0 bi\u1EBFn ch\xFAng th\xE0nh b\u1EC7 ph\xF3ng c\u1EE7a ng\u01B0\u01A1i."
    textEN: Tiny soul... fear not those jagged edges. Forge your steps into iron
      will, and make them your springboard.
    AutoSkip: 0
  AutoProgressDelay: 1.5
  TypingSpeed: 0.05
  IsActivated: 0
